{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d4309bb5cf","title":"与朝鲜同志商谈应注意方式","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"13ed97f188","index":0,"year":1950,"month":11,"day":12,"articleId":"d4309bb5cf"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji29","name":"毛泽东全集第29卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/29-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji29":{"comments":[{"id":"26fa7f7769","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"d4309bb5cf","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东给中国人民志愿军司令员兼政治委员彭德怀的电报。"},{"id":"3034f70ead","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"d4309bb5cf","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"菲利波夫，即斯大林。"}],"contents":[{"id":"080e399778","type":"title","text":"与朝鲜同志商谈应注意方式！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"d4309bb5cf"},{"id":"26fa7f7769","type":"paragraph","text":"德怀同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"d4309bb5cf"},{"id":"3034f70ead","type":"paragraph","text":"客电均悉。关于与朝鲜同志合作的各项意见都是适当的。商谈时请注意方式，采取委婉曲折的与温和的态度。并要有这样的精神准备，即有些意见通不过，争论和分岐在相当长的时期内存在着，要待打了很多的胜仗，中国同志的意见在事实上多次证明是正确的，那时才会被朝鲜同志所赞同和信服。如果情况是这样，那也是很自然的。此间拟尚菲利波天网同志有所建议，待有结果再告你。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"d4309bb5cf"},{"id":"c642adfde3","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"d4309bb5cf"},{"id":"6e6805f345","type":"paragraph","text":"十一月十二日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"d4309bb5cf"}],"page":{"id":"b8176428b0","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"d4309bb5cf","start":359,"end":359}}}},"__N_SSG":true}